snippet.title: Champion Unmasked: Katana
snippet.description:
A formidable swordswoman with a score to settle, Katana is coming soon to Infinite Crisis. Sharpen your skills, hone your blade, and prepare for the trials!

Do you want to wield the Soultaker? Then sign up and play Infinite Crisis for free at http://www.infinitecrisis.com!
